{
  "stem": "8786.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Among them was I would say about two dozen were very, very close friend of-- friends of mine from my town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This was in Balf.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One-- one of them was a-- one man, who I met in America, his son was there and he went back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And because those days, they still-- we still put on a chain or a name for each of these deceased one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Those people who were-- who died so-called naturally from fleck typhus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But these people who were just plain wiped out with the gun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they were just probably-- I read about it, that they took over to Budapest about 250 bodies and they tried to-- tried to find out who they are.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think they were very successful, because how can you figure it out?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was Balf.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now this-- now we start-- now we are at the beginning of that march, which starts from Balf.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Passover time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nights were-- the nights were-- the Russian-- Russians used to come down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They call it Stalingrad candles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you ever hear the word?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Please explain it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They light up the whole-- in middle of the night, it became so light like it is here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Huge candles and they were standing in middle of the air.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call it the Stalingrad candles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was so light, like-- at least like daytime, so they saw everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came down and they were bombing the whole Sopron.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- and naturally, the roads were full of the retreating German army, plus the Hungarian civilians, plus-- in other words, the Jewish campers, I don't know whether we were-- what we were over there, [NON-ENGLISH], whatever you call-- call us.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did not have the road for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
